OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScotland's under-18s gender
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclinic pauses puberty      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fblockers                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland's only gender identity clinic 
OL,6, for under 18s has paused prescribing   
OL,7, puberty blockers to children.          
OL,9,FThe Sandyford clinic in Glasgow also   
OL,10,Fsaid new patients aged 16 or 17 would  
OL,11,Fno longer receive other hormone        
OL,12,Ftreatments until they were 18.         
OL,14,FIt follows a landmark review of gender 
OL,15,Fservices for under-18s in England.     
OL,17,FDr Hilary Cass's review said children  
OL,18,Fhad been let down by a lack of research
OL,19,Fand there was "remarkably weak"        
OL,20,Fevidence on medical interventions.     
